---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Kalyan AI | Bespoke hosted AI systems partner"
	description="Meet Kalyan AI and how we design, build, and host bespoke AI systems with clear ownership, governance, and ongoing support for your organisation."
>
	<main class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-5xl flex-col gap-10 px-6 pb-14">
		<section class="ka-card mx-auto max-w-5xl space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">About</h1>
			<p class="copy-narrow max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg text-[var(--primary)]">
				We build and host bespoke AI systems that remove friction from core business workflows.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-4 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<div class="mx-auto aspect-[4/4.5] w-full max-w-md overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border)] shadow-sm">
				<img
					class="h-full w-full object-cover"
					src="/images/1761512653.png"
					alt="Zax Kalyan"
					loading="lazy"
					decoding="async"
					style="object-position: 50% 12%;"
				/>
			</div>

			<div class="space-y-3 text-center">
				<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Founder</h2>
				<div class="space-y-3 !text-center">
						<div class="space-y-1">
							<p class="hidden text-xs font-bold text-[var(--primary)] md:hidden">Founder background</p>
							<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)] text-center">I'm Zax Kalyan, founder of Kalyan AI. I've spent 15+ years leading and growing businesses under real-world pressure — owning P&L, building teams, and delivering results across industries.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="space-y-1">
							<p class="hidden text-xs font-bold text-[var(--primary)] md:hidden">The philosophy behind Kalyan AI</p>
							<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)] text-center">Before Kalyan AI, I started using AI systems inside my own businesses to take repetitive work off the plate: reporting, follow-ups, marketing content, social media, and the admin that quietly eats hours every week. The difference was immediate — faster turnaround, fewer mistakes, and more headspace to focus on what actually moves the business forward.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="space-y-1">
							<p class="hidden text-xs font-bold text-[var(--primary)] md:hidden">Nuvo Labs and how it informs decisions</p>
							<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)] text-center">Kalyan AI exists for one reason: to give other owner-led businesses the same benefits, without forcing them to change how they work or become "AI people". We design, build, and host bespoke systems that turn messy inputs into clear outputs — with proper control and oversight.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="space-y-1">
							<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)] text-center">I'm also a contributor and shareholder at Nuvo Labs, a deep-tech AI research company. That keeps us close to what's coming next, while staying focused on what matters day-to-day: reliability and measurable impact.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="ka-card space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
		<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">What we do</h2>
				<div class="space-y-2 !text-center">
					<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">We design, build, and operate hosted AI systems that fit your existing workflow — using your data, your tools, and clear decision ownership.</p>
					<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto text-[var(--muted)]">You stay in control. We handle the engineering, hosting, monitoring, and steady improvements.</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="ka-card p-8 my-16 text-center">
		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)] mb-6">Why hosted?</h2>
				<p class="text-[var(--muted)] mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Because you want the outcome, not an infrastructure project.</p>
				<ul class="space-y-3 text-[var(--muted)]">
					<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-3"><span class="text-[var(--primary)]">✓</span> Reliability: monitored, maintained, and supported — it doesn't silently break.</li>
					<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-3"><span class="text-[var(--primary)]">✓</span> Security + control: least-privilege access, clear data boundaries, and traceability.</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="ka-card space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
		<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">How we work</h2>
				<ol class="space-y-2 text-[var(--muted)] text-center list-none">
					<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Discover —</span> map your workflow, data, and decision points (what happens today, what "good" looks like).</li>
					<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Build —</span> implement the first high-ROI slice with safeguards and clear ownership.</li>
					<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Deploy —</span> launch with you, monitor outcomes, and stabilise fast.</li>
					<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Improve —</span> refine prompts, data flows, and reporting based on real usage.</li>
				</ol>
			</section>

			<section class="ka-card space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">What you get</h2>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-[var(--muted)] text-center list-none">
					<li>A working system in weeks (not months)</li>
					<li>Integration into your current tools (email, spreadsheets, CRM, accounting, etc.)</li>
					<li>Ongoing hosting, monitoring, and improvements</li>
					<li>Training so your team can use it day one</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="ka-card space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
		<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">What you can expect</h2>
				<ul class="space-y-2 text-[var(--muted)] text-center list-none">
					<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Clarity</span> on who decides what, and what happens next</li>
					<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Speed</span> without losing control</li>
					<li><span class="font-bold text-[var(--primary)]">Reliability</span> from a system that's maintained and supported</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

		<div class="text-center">
			<a
				class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-[var(--secondary)]"
				href="/contact#book"
				data-plausible="BookACall"
			>
				Book a call
			</a>
		</div>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
		<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">FAQs</h2>
			<div class="divide-y divide-[var(--border-subtle)] rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border-subtle)] bg-white/80 text-center">
				{[
					{
						q: 'What types of businesses do you work with?',
						a: 'Organisations where operations rely on people making repeat decisions from calls, documents, and pipelines. We focus on teams that value clarity and control.',
					},
					{
						q: 'How quickly can we ship a first version?',
						a: 'Most first versions go live in 2–4 weeks once we have access to your processes and data examples. We keep the initial scope tight to show value early.',
					},
					{
						q: 'Do you host the system for us?',
						a: 'Yes. We host, monitor, and maintain the system so you do not need extra infrastructure or support staff to keep it reliable.',
					},
					{
						q: 'What about data security and access control?',
						a: 'We set clear data boundaries, least-privilege access, and audit trails. Ownership and permissions stay defined for your team.',
					},
					{
						q: 'Can this connect to our existing tools and workflows?',
						a: 'Yes. We integrate with your current systems and processes so the hosted AI layer fits how you already work.',
					},
					{
						q: 'How do pricing and ongoing support work?',
						a: 'We scope a build fee for the first version, then provide a hosting and support plan that covers monitoring, fixes, and iterative improvements.',
					},
					{
						q: 'What do you need from us to get started?',
						a: 'Access to the people, examples, and systems that show how you work today, plus a clear owner for decisions. We handle the rest.',
					},
				].map((item) => (
					<details class="group px-4 py-3 text-[var(--muted)]">
						<summary class="flex cursor-pointer list-none items-center justify-center gap-2 text-center text-[var(--brand-navy)] font-semibold transition hover:text-[var(--brand-navy-light)] focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-[var(--primary)] focus-visible:ring-offset-0">
							<span>{item.q}</span>
							<span class="text-sm text-[var(--muted)] group-open:rotate-45 transition">+</span>
						</summary>
						<div class="pt-2 text-[var(--muted)] text-center">
							<p>{item.a}</p>
						</div>
					</details>
				))}
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
